54
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:20,680
Yes, it's very possible.

55
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,010
Quick, call Gong Sun He.

56
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,600
Alright, I understand.

57
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:29,060
We'll go there right away.

58
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,380
