59
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,040
Ms. Su,

60
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,960
we need to take these items back with us.

61
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,040
After the case is closed,

62
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:06,970
we'll notify you to retrieve them.

63
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:08,400
Officer,

64
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:10,840
when will our Lao Lin be able to come back?

65
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:13,840
We don't know that either.

66
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:16,440
Our colleagues are actively working on the rescue.

67
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,480
