73
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,560
However, we don't know if he's been found yet.

74
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:33,020
We'll notify you immediately if we find him.

75
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,520
What?

76
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:37,120
Kidnapped to an oil refinery?

77
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:39,960
It's karma!

78
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:41,560
It really is karma!

79
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:43,000
Karma!

80
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,280
What do you mean?

81
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,520
The owner of that oil refinery

82
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,720
had already

83
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:52,320
self-immolated many years ago.

84
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,760
Alright, we understand the situation.

85
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:58,960
We'll be leaving now.

86
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,840
Report: Not found.

87
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:25,280
Report: Nothing here.

88
