93
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,040
That's impossible.

94
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,840
That nursery rhyme was referring to the oil refinery.

95
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:39,100
It shouldn't be wrong.

96
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:43,120
It's almost six o'clock. It's getting light soon.

97
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,980
Sunrise is around seven o'clock.

98
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:47,659
We still have an hour. Why don't we keep looking?

99
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,120
Then search thoroughly.

100
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,650
Try to search every corner.

101
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:53,610
Let's go too.

102
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:24,440
Nothing to report.

