114
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,120
About a 40-minute drive.

115
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,800
He should be here.

116
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:53,340
But we've turned this place upside down.

117
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:55,120
We haven't found him anywhere.

118
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,000
Could it be...

119
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:58,420
