142
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:54,280
Chief.

143
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:55,340
We've found Lin Li.

144
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,410
He's right here.

145
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,380
Be careful.

146
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:20,080
This is Lin Li.

147
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:20,640
That's right.

148
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,480
This time we finally managed to

149
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,600
